sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Backend

    C->>B: Query("SELECT ...")
    B->>B: Parse / Analyze / Rewrite / Plan / Execute
    alt 返回行
        B-->>C: RowDescription
        loop 每一行
            B-->>C: DataRow
        end
    else 无行结果或命令
        B-->>C: CommandComplete
    end
    B-->>C: ReadyForQuery(I/T/E)
